==Spanish==
===Etymology===
Uncertain. If the element *''bak-'' is a metathesis of *''kab-'' (cf. French ''[[cabillaud]]'' and German ''[[Kabeljau]]'' from Dutch (''[[kabeljauw]]''), then the original form of the word could have been *''cabalao'', maybe meaning "large-headed fish".
